pdated_at`）\n   125\t  - `conversations`（`id`, `match_id`, `created_at`, `upda
ted_at`）\n   126\t  - `conversation_participants`（`id`, `conversation_id`, `us
er_id`, `last_read_message_id`, `created_at`, `updated_at`）\n   127\t  - `messa
ges`（`id`, `conversation_id`, `sender_id`, `type`, `content`, `client_message_i
