.guard.ts`，骨架逻辑如下：\n   ```typescript\n   @Injectable()\n   export class 
ProfileCompletionGuard implements CanActivate {\n     constructor(@InjectReposit
ory(UserProfileEntity) private repo: Repository<UserProfileEntity>) {}\n     asy
nc canActivate(context: ExecutionContext): Promise<boolean> {\n       const req 
= context.switchToHttp().getRequest();\n       const profile = await this.repo.f
indOne({ where: { user_id: req.user?.userId } });\n       if (!profile?.is_compl
ete) throw new BusinessException(1000, \'Please complete your profile first.\');
\n       return true;\n     }\n   }\n   ```\n\n5. **问题**：`AuthController` 实
现与 `docs/api-contracts/auth.yaml` 契约不一致\n   **建议**：修改 `apps/api/src/
modules/auth/auth.controller.ts`：\n   - `POST /auth/login` 应接收 `LoginRequest
`（`phone` + `sms_code`），而非单独的 `register` + `login` 入口；\n   - 若基础设
