me, \'../database/entities/*.entity{.ts,.js}\'),\n     join(__dirname, \'../modu
les/**/*.entity{.ts,.js}\'),\n   ],\n   ```\n\n9. **问题**：`docs/api-contracts/
auth.yaml` 的 `LoginResponse` 缺少 `is_new_user` 字段（与 `TASK-Auth-Login` 决策
冲突）\n   **建议**：在 `auth.yaml` 的 `LoginResponse` 组件中增加：\n   ```yaml\
n   is_new_user:\n     type: boolean\n   ```\n   并同步运行 `make generate-types
` 更新 `packages/shared-types/` 与 `apps/mobile/lib/models/generated/`。\n\n10. 
