ller("auth")`.\n2. **DataSource entities path incorrect**: `data-source.ts` poin
ts to `../modules/**/*.entity` but core entities are in `../database/entities/`.
This breaks `make db:migrate` and `migration:generate` CLI commands.\n3. **AuthC
ontroller implementation mismatches OpenAPI contract**: Contract defines `POST /
auth/login` with `phone` + `sms_code`, but controller has a separate `register` 
endpoint with `birth_date` and a stub `login` with no body.\n4. **RegisterDto la
cks validation decorators**: Violates `docs/design-docs/nestjs.md` which require
s `class-validator` + `class-transformer` on all DTOs.\n5. **Missing JWT Auth Gu
ard**: `docs/modules/auth.md` references `apps/api/src/common/guards/jwt-auth.gu
ard.ts` but it doesn\'t exist.\n6. **Missing ProfileCompletionGuard**: Required 
by TASK-Profile execution plan but not implemented.\n\n**Major:**\n7. **Admin da
shboard API base URL mismatch**: `apps/admin/src/lib/api.ts` uses `http://localh
ost:3001` without `/api/v1` prefix, but API routes are prefixed with `/api/v1`.\
n8. **OpenAPI auth contract missing `is_new_user`**: Explicitly required in TASK
-Auth-Login plan.\n9. **`make build` tries to build design-system as APK**: `pac
kages/design-system` is a Flutter package, not an app. `flutter build apk --debu
g` will fail for it.\n10. **QUALITY_SCORE.md severely outdated**: Claims most ar
eas are "❌ 未开始" but this PR implements them.\n11. **BDD step definitions are
all empty skeletons**: While infrastructure bootstrap allows skeletons, the step
